- Oh, no.
- Oh my gosh.

39:09.588 --> 39:11.434
- [Joanna] Whoa.

39:11.434 --> 39:12.760
- [Dusty] Oh wow, yeah.

39:12.760 --> 39:14.135
That's too good.

39:14.135 --> 39:15.003
- Wow.

