39:32.278 --> 39:33.759
- I'm completely excited

39:33.759 --> 39:36.261
and ready to start doing music outdoors,

39:36.261 --> 39:37.711
and I think it's really
gonna be a great way

39:37.711 --> 39:42.340
for the Lodge and the restaurant
and the music to unite.

39:42.340 --> 39:43.435
- Wow!
- Perfect.

