- They will.

41:15.134 --> 41:16.034
- Good luck, okay?

41:16.034 --> 41:17.508
- Thank you so much.

41:17.508 --> 41:20.991
There's just no words that can
express how grateful I feel

41:20.991 --> 41:23.535
