41:23.535 --> 41:24.404
- [Gordon] Good night, darling.

41:24.404 --> 41:25.272
- Bye-bye.

41:26.246 --> 41:27.438
- I'll be sad to leave this place,

41:27.438 --> 41:29.291
but I will not be sorry

41:29.291 --> 41:31.366
